nch <i>perce(r)</i> ‘pierce’ + <i>val</i> ‘valley’. This may well have been influenced by   Percy  , which was similarly analysed as a compound of <i>perce(r)</i> ‘pierce’ + <i>haie</i> ‘hedge’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Percival Toukere was born in 1329, in France as the son of Sir Percival le Toukere. He had at least 1 son with Augusta Jane. He died in 1360, at the age of 31, and was buried in France."},"et":{"1329–1360":"1329–1360","1306–Female":"1306–Surnud","1358–1384":"1358–1384","1301–1320":"1301–1320","1358":"1358","1301":"1301","1320":"1320","1384":"1384","1360":"1360","1329":"1329","1306":"1306","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1329–1360":"1329–1360","1306–Female":"1306–Kuollut","1358–1384":"1358–1384","1301–1320":"1301–1320","1358":"1358","1301":"1301","1320":"1320","1384":"1384","1360":"1360","1329":"1329","1306":"1306","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"1329–1360":"1329–1360","1306–Female":"1306–Décédée","1358–1384":"1358–1384","1301–1320":"1301–1320","1358":"1358","1301":"1301","1320":"1320","1384":"1384","1360":"1360","1329":"1329","1306":"1306","France":"France","lifeSummary":"John Percival Toukere est né en 1329, à France, fils de Sir Percival le Toukere. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Augusta Jane. Il est décédé en 1360, à l’âge de 31 ans, et a été enterré à France."},"de":{"1329–1360":"1329–1360","1306–Female":"1306–Verstorben","1358–1384":"1358–1384","1301–1320":"1301–1320","1358":"1358","1301":"1301","1320":"1320","1384":"1384","1360":"1360","1329":"1329","1306":"1306","France":"Frankreich","lifeSummary":"John Percival Toukere wurde 1329 in Frankreich, als Sohn von Sir Percival le Toukere geboren. Er hatte mit Augusta Jane mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1360 im Alter von 31 Jahren und wurde in Frankreich begraben."},"ht":{"1329–1360":"1329–1360","1306–Female":"1306–Desede","1358–1384":"1358–1384","1301–1320":"1301–1320","1358":"1358","1301":"1301","1320":"1320","1384":"1384","1360":"1360","1329":"1329","1306":"1306","France":"France"},"hu":{"1329–13